<p class="entry-meta"><time class="entry-time" itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2018-11-27T00:00:12+00:00">November 27, 2018</time> <span class="entry-by">by</span> <span class="entry-author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/author/lace/" class="entry-author-link" itemprop="url" rel="author"><span class="entry-author-name" itemprop="name">Lace</span></a></span> </p></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><figure id="attachment_3997" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-3997" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway.jpg" alt="How To Set Live Wallpaper On iPhone (A Complete User Guide) | Joy of Apple" width="700" height="420" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway.jpg 1000w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway-300x180.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway-768x461.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-3997" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway.jpg" alt="How To Set Live Wallpaper On iPhone (A Complete User Guide) | Joy of Apple" width="700" height="420" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway.jpg 1000w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway-300x180.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Win-an-iPhone-XS-Max-iDrop-News-Apple-iPhone-XS-Max-Giveaway-768x461.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">How To Set Live Wallpaper On iPhone (A Complete User Guide)</figcaption></figure>
<p>iPhone 6s and up has a live feature that brings lock screen wallpapers to a whole new level. Knowing how to set live wallpaper on iPhone will surely give you an edge over others.</p><div class='code-block code-block-1' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="1994154162"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<p>The live feature was an instant hit ever since its first introduction. I personally only have live lock screen wallpapers on my iPhone to make use of this amazing feature.</p>
<p>But before getting into the steps for setting live wallpaper on our iPhones, let us first go over what a live wallpaper is!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/dynamic-wallpaper-for-iphone/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Related: How To Setup Dynamic Wallpapers On iPhone!</a></strong></p><div class='code-block code-block-2' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="4728128714"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">What Is The iPhone Live Feature?</h2>
<p>The live feature lets you have a lock screen wallpaper that moves when you press it. But just to be clear, it is not a video, rather it is a picture. And that is what makes it mysteriously amazing.</p>
<figure id="attachment_4007" style="width: 225px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="//giphy.com/gifs/fish-IjQvZPkEbM3pS&quot;&gt;via GIPHY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4007 size-full" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/giphy.gif" alt="Live Fish Wallpaper" width="225" height="401" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4007 size-full" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/giphy.gif" alt="Live Fish Wallpaper" width="225" height="401" /></noscript></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Live Fish Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>Even better, you can also take live photos for yourself with your iPhone camera. Apple has really stepped up its game with their smartphones.</p>
<p>Now that you know what a live wallpaper looks like, let&#8217;s learn how to set it up on your iPhone!</p><div class='code-block code-block-3' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:block" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5677971237301931" data-ad-slot="8531642354" data-ad-format="link" data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How To Set Live Wallpaper On iPhone</h2>
<p>There are two methods for setting live wallpapers on your iPhone.</p>
<h3>Method 1: Through iPhone Settings</h3>
<p>Because Apple has incorporated this feature, they have also added built-in live wallpapers for you to choose from. Mind you, these wallpapers are even more stunning as your lock screen wallpaper.</p>
<p>These live wallpapers vary from iPhone to iPhone. Check out the steps on how to set up these built-in wallpapers through iPhone settings.</p>
<p><strong>Launch iPhone Settings and go to &#8216;Wallpaper&#8217;.</strong> <strong>Click on &#8216;Choose a New Wallpaper&#8217; to see your phone&#8217;s available options for home and lock screen wallpapers. </strong></p>
<figure id="attachment_4012" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4012" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-1024x576.png" alt="Method 1: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4012" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-1024x576.png" alt="Method 1: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1-1-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Method 1: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>You will then see choices of wallpapers and even have access to your own gallery of photos. <strong>Select built-in Live photos</strong>. You will then get a preview of what the wallpaper would look like on your lock screen.</p>
<p>Make sure that the &#8216;Live Photo&#8217; option is selected so you get its full effect. <strong>Tap &#8216;Set&#8217; and select &#8216;Set Lock Screen&#8217;.</strong></p>
<figure id="attachment_4013" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4013" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-1024x576.png" alt="Method 1: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4013" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-1024x576.png" alt="Method 1: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Untitled-design-2-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Method 1: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>And just like that, you have successfully set a live wallpaper to your lock screen. <strong>All you need to do now is firmly press on the wallpaper and it will do its magic.</strong></p>
<figure id="attachment_4015" style="width: 300px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4015" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-576x1024.png" alt="Live Wallpaper On Lock Screen" width="300" height="534" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-576x1024.png 576w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-169x300.png 169w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572.png 750w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4015" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-576x1024.png" alt="Live Wallpaper On Lock Screen" width="300" height="534" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-576x1024.png 576w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572-169x300.png 169w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/IMG_5572.png 750w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Live Wallpaper On Lock Screen</figcaption></figure>
<h3>Method 2: Through iPhone Photos</h3>
<figure id="attachment_4016" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4016" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-1024x683.jpg" alt="iPhone 6s And Up - Live Camera Feature" width="700" height="467" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-300x200.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-768x512.jpg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-600x400.jpg 600w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4016" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-1024x683.jpg" alt="iPhone 6s And Up - Live Camera Feature" width="700" height="467" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-300x200.jpg 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-768x512.jpg 768w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462-600x400.jpg 600w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/dsc2462.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">iPhone 6s And Up &#8211; Live Camera Feature</figcaption></figure>
<p>Because of the live feature, the iPhone has the ability to record a live photo as well. Make sure that the Live Camera is turned on before snapping a photo. After that, you can find these shots on your Photos gallery.</p>
<p><strong>Launch Photos and select &#8216;Camera Roll&#8217;. </strong>Look for the live photos you just took so you can set it up as your lock screen wallpaper.</p>
<figure id="attachment_4017" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4017" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4017" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/3-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Method 2: Part 1 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>After selecting the live photo you wish to set as lock screen wallpaper, <strong>tap the options icon below. Select &#8216;Use as Wallpaper&#8217;.</strong></p>
<figure id="attachment_4018" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4018" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4018" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/4-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Method 2: Part 2 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<p>The last part of this method should go seamlessly. <strong>Click on &#8216;Set&#8217; and make sure that the photo is on &#8216;Live Photo&#8217;. Select &#8216;Set Lock Screen&#8217; to set it as your wallpaper</strong>. Then, press firmly on the lock screen to animate the wallpaper.</p>
<figure id="attachment_4019" style="width: 700px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="lazy lazy-hidden wp-image-4019" src="//joyofapple.com/wp-content/plugins/a3-lazy-load/assets/images/lazy_placeholder.gif" data-lazy-type="image" data-src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 3 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="" data-srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /><noscript><img class="wp-image-4019" src="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-1024x576.png" alt="Method 2: Part 3 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper" width="700" height="394" srcset="https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-1024x576.png 1024w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-300x169.png 300w, https://joyofapple.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/5-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></noscript><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">Method 2: Part 3 Of Setting Up Live Photo For Wallpaper</figcaption></figure>
<h2>FAQs</h2>
<h3>1. How Can I Get Custom Live Wallpapers on iPhone X?</h3>
<p>Nothing is more personalized than taking your own live photos on your iPhone. But, you can also use third-party apps that give you amazing live wallpapers as well.</p>
<p>Most of these apps offer a wide range of wallpapers for you to choose from.</p>
<p>Your iPhone will never have a bare lock screen again! <strong><a href="https://joyofapple.com/blog/best-free-and-paid-iphone-x-live-wallpapers-apps/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Check out our list of the best live wallpapers apps for iPhone X!</a></strong></p>
<h3>3. Can I Set Videos on My Lock Screen?</h3>
<p>At the moment, your iPhone doesn&#8217;t support setting videos as your lock screen. If your iPhone is jailbroken then there is an unofficial, third-party app that you can use called <strong>vWallpaper</strong>. Just remember, a jailbroken phone loses its warranty.</p>
<p>But for the meantime, the closest you can get to a moving wallpaper is a live one!</p>
<h2>Live And Animated Wallpapers On iPhone</h2>
<p>It&#8217;s amazing how the iPhone has stepped up their wallpaper game from traditional still-photos to moving ones. If you ever want to animate your lock screen, follow the steps above and you&#8217;ll be good to go!</p>
<p>Have fun choosing live wallpapers for your iPhone!</p>
<p><strong>What do you think of the iPhone&#8217;s live feature? Do you take your own Live pictures for your wallpaper, or do you prefer using apps or the built-in options? Let us know in the comments section below!</strong></p>
